 thub.io
DTSTAMP:20260713T161321Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260901
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260902
SUMMARY:Deadline: Emerging Talents: Production Grant (Design)
DESCRIPTION:Pro Helvetia's Emerging Talents production grant supports the p
 roduction of design projects based on completed prototypes or sample colle
 ctions. Emerging Talents are professional designers whose training or busi
 ness registration dates back less than seven years. ELIGIBILITY: requires 
 a connection to Switzerland (Swiss citizenship\, or permanent residency wi
 th regular artistic activity in Switzerland)\; not open to practitioners w
 ithout a Swiss connection. At least 50 percent of participants must be Swi
 ss citizens or permanent residents whose place of work is in Switzerland. 
 AMOUNT: up to CHF 50\,000\, on condition that own or third-party funding i
 s available. Deadlines twice a year: 1 March (23:59 CET) and 1 September (
 23:59 CEST). Apply via the Pro Helvetia portal.\n\nOrganisation: Pro Helve
 tia (Swiss Arts Council)\nLocation: Switzerland-based emerging designers.\
 nAward: Up to CHF 50\,000\, conditional on own or third-party matching fun
 ding. No application fee.\nDuration: Production phase\; deadlines twice ye
 arly (1 March and 1 September).\n\nMore: https://prohelvetia.ch/en/find-su
 pport/emerging-talents-production-grant?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantd
 esk&utm_medium=referral
